There are several useful macros, and many more to come I'm sure, that store data in OS_PROPERTYENTRY.  Currently there is no way to delete an entry from the table so entries that are no longer needed are being set to null and left to clutter up the database.  I'd like a method made available in the api that allows entries that are no longer needed to be removed from the table.

